title: THREADS - Broken Homme
description: There's a certain elegance in finely-made goods. And this is especially true for the shoes and boots crafted by Broken Homme. Made in America, the brand's footwear pays homage to the past with a relevancy that places it in the spotlight today. At Stance, we're honored to partner with Broken Homme to create a sock worthy of the brand's boots—the Higgs... check it out here - http://www.stance.com/shop/higgs
